data.title: Full Match | Hangzhou Spark vs Guangzhou Charge | Overwatch League 2020 | Week 8 | Day 2

data.title: 雷霆万钧：旧金山震动队的冠军皮肤
data.description: 《守望先锋》游戏设计师揭示了传奇末日铁拳皮肤“雷霆”的设计和功能，该皮肤旨在庆祝旧金山震动队夺得2019年赛季冠军，并在Blizzcon 2019上让Sinatraa、Moth和Super先睹为快。

data.title: Top 5 Plays of Week 5: Jjonak's Instant Sleep Dart Is on Target
data.description: The first week of Hero Pool produced a spectacle of pure chaos in Washington, D.C. We got a lot of Sombra play, which meant a lot of Jjonak hitting unthinkable Sleep Darts. Winston got his time to shine and Roar made sure to capitalize on Eichenwalde. Meanwhile, Blasé’s Doomfist continued to reign supreme.

data.title: Full Match | Boston Uprising vs Atlanta Reign | Overwatch League 2020 | Week 5 | Day 2
data.description: Week 5 of the 2020 Overwatch League season is live from Washington D.C. on March 7 and March 8 on YouTube Gaming. The two-day homestand features the Toronto Defiant, Florida Mayhem, Paris Eternal, Houston Outlaws, Boston Uprising, Philadelphia Fusion, New York Excelsior and Atlanta Reign. Will the Fusion put down Paris Eternal to remain undefeated? Can the Justice make up for their last homestand and win at home? Tune in to find out!

data.title: Full Match | London Spitfire vs Washington Justice | Overwatch League 2020 | Week 3 | Day 2
data.description:
Week 3 of the 2020 Overwatch League season is live from Washington D.C. on February 22 and 23 on YouTube Gaming. The two-day homestand features the Washington Justice, New York Excelsior, Philadelphia Fusion, Boston Uprising, Houston Outlaws, Paris Eternal, Toronto Defiant, and London Spitfire. Will the Excelsior or the Fusion make that first place spot their own? Can the Spitfire or the Outlaws get their first win of the season? Tune in to find out!
